{"tid":1030581,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都覺得Retrofuturism好正？","createTime":"2019-02-21T05:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T17:15:19.000Z","uid":161684,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c8555a2795bb94cbd42cc69a01bb0fc2db2061ab","tid":1030581,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T05:04:53.000Z","msg":"睇科學館翻新嘅post醒起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢種風格咁樣歸類唔知啱唔啱<br />\n講緊嘅係以前人對未來嘅想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uMh27ow.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuMh27ow.png&h=4d7637ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(~1970s, Ralph McQuarrie)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iveMPxd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiveMPxd.png&h=1b5a69c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(~1970s, from NASA Ames Research Centre)</span><br />\n<br />\n又或者將某種美學喺未來嘅框架下復興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6KgLkxU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6KgLkxU.png&h=de51f08b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(2018, James Gilleard)</span><br />\n<br />\n最好J係可以比較下多年後現實中嘅科技發展<br />\n可能方向差唔多 但細節迥異<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qzu1Dyz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqzu1Dyz.png&h=7c24c963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLSKBoP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLSKBoP.png&h=42af79f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wrBzdOJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwrBzdOJ.png&h=dc86f96d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(1981, Robert Tinney)</span><br />\n<br />\n就好似窺探到一個平行時空咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5dad593e558bbdb8cde28fb1ab6e4330e63d94","tid":1030581,"uid":50658,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T05:09:02.000Z","msg":"第四張圖諗起俾女人揸車就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf71d4960abf8859be71907da2c85eba2c9e3c3","tid":1030581,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3ff91513072825973966ca1372bf17ed6beb49","tid":1030581,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://m.imgur.com/TgPAwIw?r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.imgur.com%2FTgPAwIw%3Fr&h=cd3936b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f278b08ecfe4c413d985d22a22e1d631855ae53","tid":1030581,"uid":59832,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPDFboQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPDFboQ.jpg&h=3d40101a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a869d9c8338d83c21d9c13b22f63137db3775a7","tid":1030581,"uid":151847,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:03:06.000Z","msg":"有 好靚 好鍾意睇以前嘅人對未來既幻想"},{"pid":"17012379306601d3b5c30e00b13467ee767f95fb","tid":1030581,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:38:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zj5wjAR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzj5wjAR.png&h=676b1842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb576d749c8d058b300e3b6f99fd9d42be2f6d5","tid":103058